Text Adventure Engine specs
---------------------------

2026-03: R0S (release 0 for the SENTINEL R0):
- runs from RAM
- uses CLI keyboard handling
- minor bug fixes and code optimizations

2023-10: R0P (release 0 for the PIONEER R1):
- tiny text adventure engine
- runs on a 16-character display
- the descriptive text is short and the dictionary is limited
- simple parser understands one and two word commands made of verb and noun
- the focus lies on solving puzzles, the atmosphere is secondary
- no time limit and no score
- 5-bit packed chars:
  26 capital letters, 4 punctuation symbols and 2 special chars CR and EOS
- only first letter of verb and noun are used so unique, unambiguous verb/noun
  combinations are required for each location

